    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-26T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="1155"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1155">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">860c.24/7–2645: Telegram</note>
                <head>No. 1155<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Assistant Secretary of State</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="#p_CWL1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clayton</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Army–Navy Liquidation Commissioner</hi>
                        (<persName corresp="#p_MTB1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">McCabe</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d1155fn1">Sent to the Acting Secretary of State
                        over the signature of <persName corresp="#p_BJF1">Byrnes</persName>.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Babelsberg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-26">July 26,
                            1945</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Victory1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Victory</hi>
                    </gloss> 349. To [Acting] Secretary of State Washington for <persName
                        corresp="#p_MTB1">McCabe</persName> from <persName corresp="#p_CWL1"
                        >Clayton</persName>[;] for <persName corresp="#p_FFW1">Fetter</persName>
                    from <persName corresp="#p_CEG1">Collado</persName>.</p>
                <p>Please inform us urgently of status of 1,000 trucks for Poland. …<note n="2"
                        xml:id="d1155fn2">Cf. <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_403">p.
                            403</ref>.</note>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
